{{ 'ka-collection-intro.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

{%- comment -%}
  K&A Collection Intro
  Spec: Docs/collection-build-spec.md, Section 2 ("Section 4 — Collection Intro"), F3.
  Editorial description + a facts strip (Silhouettes / Made to Order / Price Range /
  Sizing) that replaces a filter sidebar with the information a bride actually needs.

  All five values are collection-level metafields (namespace "custom"):
    custom.intro_copy, custom.silhouettes, custom.lead_time,
    custom.price_range_display, custom.sizing_note
  Per scope boundary #2 of this build: where the spec has not drafted real copy yet
  (The Festive Edit, Barre Oblique), the metafield will be blank in Admin until
  Creative Director supplies it. The Liquid below falls back to an explicitly
  temporary scaffolding string in that case, rather than inventing brand copy.
  Per CD Note 4 (spec Section 7): price range is always a manually maintained
  metafield string, never computed from collection.products min/max.
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="ka-coll-intro">
  <p class="ka-coll-intro__body reveal">
    {{ collection.metafields.custom.intro_copy | default: "Intro copy pending — Creative Director, see collection-build-spec.md §4" }}
  </p>
  <div class="ka-coll-intro__facts reveal reveal-delay-1">
    <div>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-label">Silhouettes</p>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-value">{{ collection.metafields.custom.silhouettes | default: "Pending — see §4" }}</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-label">Made to Order</p>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-value">{{ collection.metafields.custom.lead_time | default: "Pending — see §4" }}</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-label">Price Range</p>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-value">{{ collection.metafields.custom.price_range_display | default: "Pending — see §4" }}</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-label">Sizing</p>
      <p class="ka-coll-intro__fact-value">{{ collection.metafields.custom.sizing_note | default: "Made to Measure" }}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Collection Intro",
  "tag": "div",
  "class": "ka-collection-intro-section",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Content for this section is pulled from collection metafields (namespace custom: intro_copy, silhouettes, lead_time, price_range_display, sizing_note), not from settings here — edit per collection in Shopify Admin > Collections > [collection] > Metafields."
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    { "name": "Collection Intro" }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
